summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easement deed and grant of easement over portion of 17th Ave. W. and portions of Government Lot 4 in Section 23, Township 25 North, Range 3 East, W.M. of W. Garfield St. and of Joliet Ave. W. for storm drain and outfall purposes (Queen Anne Ave. W., et al., Sewer Separation) and for sanitary sewer purposes. (Dartmouth Ave. W., et al, Sanitary Sewer).
